<h3 id="submission-instructions">Submission Instructions</h3>

<p>Papers can be submitted at <a href="https://www.scomminc.com/pcm/wfiot/wfiot.cfm">https://www.scomminc.com/pcm/wfiot/wfiot.cfm</a>, choosing ‘A Technical Paper,’ then in the field ‘First choice of paper assignment’ select ‘Workshops’ and choose ‘Work-09’ in the track field. Papers should be six (6) pages in length. The conference allows up to two additional pages for a maximum length of eight (8) pages with payment of extra page charges once the paper has been accepted.</p>
